%~ \textbf{7. acACxnakiSx duyxmatatxmoV} \hfill{\bf puTa \pageref{113}}
%~ 
%~ \hfill{teY. saM 1-5-6-10}
%~ 
%~ niVnu vasumaMtanAgididxVye. vasugaLu saha hogaLuva kiVtiRvaMtanAgididxVye. aMtaha niVnu diVpitxmaMtanAgi, parxkAshamayanAgidudx nanage dhana-puruSAthaRvanunx aBimuKanAgidudx (acACx) anugarxhisu.
