%~ \textbf{33. AdiBUtashacx vaNoVR meV} \hfill{5 sholxVkagaLu puTa \pageref{157}}
%~ 
%~ \hfill{lakiSxmXVtaMtarx 50-138 riMda 142ra varege.}
%~ 
%~ nanage (shirxVdeVvige) vAcakavAguvaMtaha shabadxgaLalilx modalaneyadAda vanaRvu parxNavAgidudx adaralilxya shAMta udita AnaMda rUpavAda BeVdagaLalilx idUdx A nananx savxrUpadiMdaleV nAnu AnaMdamayiyAgiruvenu.
%~ 
%~ teYladhAreyaMte aviciCxnanxvAda, diVGaRvAgi moLaguva GaMTAnAda rUpavAda parxNavada sUkaSxmXvAda A shiKeyu - tudiyu nananx shabadxmayavAda deVhavAgide.
%~ 
%~ A nAdabarxhamxdalilx cenAnxgi muLuguvavanu Aditayx vaNaRsamUhavAda shabadxmayavAda nananxnunx shiVGarxvAgi seVrutAtxne.
%~ 
%~ shAMtApashAyxdi rUpadiMda vanaRgaLanunx dhavxni mADuva veYKariyu sakala padAthaRgaLanunx karedukoDuva kAmadhevnuvAgide.
