%~ AkAshadalilx saMBavisuva nAdavu anAhataveMdu kareyalapxDutatxde. AroVhadalilx AhatanAdavU avaroVhadalilx anAhata nAdavU uMTAguvudu.
%~ 
%~ A nAdavanunx SaDAjxdi savxragaLiMda ELu viBAga mADidAdxre. SaDajx, QuSaBa, gAMdhAra, madhayxma, paMcama, dheYvata, niSAdagaLeMba ELu savxragaLanUnx maniVSigaLu heVLutAtxre.
